text: Calle Järnkrok (born 25 September 1991), nicknamed "Ironhook"Järnkrok's nickname is a direct translation of his last name into English. is a Swedish professional ice hockey player. He currently plays for the Seattle Kraken of the National Hockey League (NHL). ==References== Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish ice hockey centres Category:Nashville Predators players Category:Seattle Kraken players
